    <item>
      <title>干燥的加沙居民称赞来自埃及的水“像糖”</title>
      <link>https://www.reuters.com/world/middle-east/parched-gaza-residents-praise-water-tasting-like-sugar-egypt-2023-12-21/</link>
      <description><![CDATA[对于加沙居民扎基·阿布·斯莱马来说，以色列数周的轰炸和围困让他和其他许多人喝着不干净的咸水，现在从埃及海水淡化项目流入这片被毁的飞地的水尝起来“像糖”。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.reuters.com/world/middle-east/parched-gaza-residents-praise-water-tasting-like-sugar-egypt-2023-12-21/</guid>
      <pubDate>Thu, 21 Dec 2023 13:46:37 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>巴基斯坦伊姆兰·汗律师在定罪上诉失败后仍被禁止投票</title>
      <link>https://www.reuters.com/world/asia-pacific/imran-khans-appeal-against-conviction-rejected-by-pakistan-court-lawyer-says-2023-12-21/</link>
      <description><![CDATA[巴基斯坦前总理伊姆兰·汗的律师表示，在法院驳回了他周四暂缓先前定罪的请求后，他仍然被取消竞选选举的资格。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.reuters.com/world/asia-pacific/imran-khans-appeal-against-conviction-rejected-by-pakistan-court-lawyer-says-2023-12-21/</guid>
      <pubDate>Thu, 21 Dec 2023 12:33:04 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
